Dvd arrived nicely with no damage and the art on the cover is also nice.Because their father transfers to Sapporo, Todo Yuto and Todo Eirika begin to live alone. They are siblings but they are not blood related. When Yuto was a child, his mother died, and his father remarried. Because of this, Yuto had a new mother and a sister, Erika. His new mother was quite gentle and made a lasting effect on him, but she died, too. (His sister makes fun of him always holding onto and looking at a photo of his mother who was very gifted herself. She makes fun of him saying that he always looks at her photo because of his jugs.) Living alone, Yuto and Erika begin to love as man and woman. However, Sayaka, Yuto's art teacher notices their relations, and takes an interest in Yuto and what's going on......
